Female. Mean body length: 4 ± 0.8 mm , mean head length: 0.3 ± 0.1 mm (n= 2 ). Antenna 1 similar in shape to male, flagellum with 10 articles; antenna 2 similar in shape to male, flagellum with 7 articles. Gnathopod 1 (
